						by <a href="http://www.chickadvisor.com/articles/siofan/">Siofan</a></div></div><br class="clear"><div id="article_content"><img alt="" style="margin: 5px;" src="http://images.chickadvisor.com/article/5468/original/ab00295f40f0c04f88a8ab12d38857c5.jpg"><br>We&#39;re still <a target="_blank" href="http://www.chickadvisor.com/article/spring-must-have-the-trench-coat/">majorly crushing on trench coats this spring</a>, but for those days when we want something more sporty, we&#39;re opting for the city safari anorak. In muted khaki, washed tan and deep navy these coats pair well with bright colours or muted neutrals. Whether you go short or long, this slouchy jacket will be a piece you&#39;ll wear again in the fall.<br><br><img alt="" style="margin: 5px;" src="http://images.chickadvisor.com/article/5468/original/f2c3ac6cfbf0a79456504a6333d341c4.jpg"><br>These short anoraks and safari toppers can take on whatever shape you like, cinch in for a fitted shape or leave it loose and slouchy. We love them with the sleeves rolled up and paired with a summer scarf.<br>1. Mango Cropped Fitted J Saint <a target="_blank" href="http://shop.mango.com/ficha.faces?id=43106775&state=she_404_IN">C$139.90</a><br>2. Zara Studio Safari Jacket <a target="_blank" href="http://www.zara.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/product/ca/en/zara-S2011/61135/330529/STUDIO%2BSAFARI%2BJACKET">C$159.00</a><br>3. Gap Lightweight Utility Jacket <a target="_blank" href="http://www.gapcanada.ca/browse/product.do?cid=5739&vid=1&pid=827925">C$89.95</a><br>4. Banana Republic Patch Pocket Shirt Jacket <a target="_blank" href="http://bananarepublic.gapcanada.ca/browse/product.do?cid=40924&vid=1&pid=832726">C$124.00</a><br>5. Maison Scotch Short Parka With Drawstring Waist <a target="_blank" href="http://www.asos.com/Maison-Scotch/Maison-Scotch-Short-Parka-With-Drawstring-Waist/Prod/pgeproduct.aspx?iid=1525992&cid=2641&sh=0&pge=0&pgesize=200&sort=-1&clr=Navy">C$329.49</a><br>6. Lauren By Ralph Lauren Maribel Taffeta Anorak <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thebay.com/eng/women/coatsjackets-Maribel_Taffeta_Anorak-thebay/188308">C$167.30</a><br><br><img alt="" style="margin: 5px;" src="http://images.chickadvisor.com/article/5468/original/a306acb31ef286566cb6f8e5ae16d3a6.jpg"><br>A longer, parka-style anorak will keep you dry on rainy days with no fussy belt to fiddle with. Over-sized pockets can even stash an umbrella between showers.<br>1. Mango Trench Coat Trendy <a target="_blank" href="http://shop.mango.com/ficha.faces?id=41015353&state=she_404_IN">C$254.90</a><br>2. Billabong Sergeant <a target="_blank" href="http://www.billabonggirls-usa.com/product-cat/177/jackets#item_1492_sergeant-">C$68.00</a><br>3. H&M Parka <a target="_blank" href="http://www.hm.com/ca/product/82160?article=82160-A#cm_vc=SIMILAR_TO_PD">C$59.95</a><br>4. Asos Sweat Parka <a target="_blank" href="http://www.asos.com/Asos/Asos-Sweat-Parka/Prod/pgeproduct.aspx?iid=1390078&cid=2641&sh=0&pge=0&pgesize=200&sort=-1&clr=Grey">C$106.86</a><br>5. Anthropologie Influential Anorak <a target="_blank" href="http://www.anthropologie.com/anthro/catalog/productdetail.jsp?id=20294989&catId=CLOTHES-COATS&pushId=CLOTHES-COATS&popId=CLOTHES&navAction=top&navCount=12&color=020&isProduct=true&fromCategoryPage=true&isSubcategory=true&subCategoryId=CLOTHES-COATS&templateType=subCategory">C$128.00</a><br>6. Michael Michael Kors Zip Anorak <a target="_blank" href="http://www.michaelkors.com/store/catalog/prod.jhtml?itemId=prod9820006&parentId=cat19301&masterId=cat102&index=6&cmCat=cat000000cat102cat19301">C$170.00</a><br><br>What&#39;s your go-to spring jacket like?</div><br class="clear">
